<section id="FAQ">
<h2>FAQs</h2>
<h3>Where is Stonehaugh Lamp Co. based?</h3>
<p>We are based in Stonehaugh, Northumberland which is a small hamlet on the edge of Kielder Forest Park.</p>
<h3>How can I buy your products?</h3>
<p>We currently have items available for purchase on <a href="https://www.numonday.com/shop/stonehaugh-lamp-company-store/">numonday</a> and <a href="https://upcite.co.uk/pages/seller-profile?stonehaugh-lamp-co">Upcite</a>.</p>
